contents.main: Great effort springs naturally from great attitude.
A positive attitude can really make dreams come true – it did for me.
You have a problem with my attitude and that’s not my problem.
You can have RESULTS or EXCUSES, not both.
A bad attitude is like a flat tire, you won’t get anywhere till you change it.
Attitude is a little thing that makes a big difference.
A strong and positive attitude creates more miracles than any other thing because life is 10% how u make it and 90% how u take it!
